Project Description

A Pomodoro (http://pomodorotechnique.com/) style timer.

Requirements

A single page timer application with a count down timer function.

The duration of the timer should be configurable.
  * Experiment with different configuration methods,
    * (e.g. select drop down box,
    * or field for entering the value,
    * or up and down arrow that adjust a value).

There should be a place to put Notes to Self (sometimes called Task Reminder).

There should be controls
  * Pause
  * Complete
  * Abort

No historical information will be kept (no backend)

The product should be delivered in multiple, tagged, versions.

Start with a minimum viable product.  The first product should be just a page that when loaded starts a 20 minute count down timer.
